Dive into the forefront of innovative healthcare with Sense7ai Healthcare Division, your gateway to a transformative career in immunology. We are your conduit to a fulfilling journey with a confidential client devoted to advancing patient care through cutting-edge, targeted therapies. This position will directly report to the Client, who is located in the US.&nbsp;
Your Impact: As a champion in immunology, you will be the linchpin in a quest to revolutionize patient outcomes. Armed with a robust pipeline of dermatological and immunological treatments, including breakthrough approaches for SLE, psoriasis, and uveitis, your mission is to steer from conventional immunosuppression toward a future of precise, patient-tailored care.&nbsp;
Your Arena:&nbsp;

Engage with a network of medical and scientific elites, sparking pivotal conversations that shape the healthcare landscape.&nbsp;
Scout and spotlight investigative sites and key opinion leaders, fostering groundbreaking clinical studies.&nbsp;
Provide critical data and insight that propel the utility and distinction of clinet's therapeutic arsenal, influencing clinical practices far and wide.&nbsp;

Your Essence:&nbsp;

You're an erudite with an Advanced Clinical/Science Degree (MD, DO, PharmD, PhD, PA), and 2+ years in Medical Affairs within pharma.&nbsp;
A connoisseur of the medical community, you bring a wealth of knowledge on customer segments and market dynamics.&nbsp;
Your communication prowess is unmatched, whether presenting complex data or engaging in scientific discourse.&nbsp;

Your Edge:&nbsp;

Doctoral-level candidates (MD, PharmD, DO, PhD) with a flair for Immunology/Rheumatology will stand out.&nbsp;
A wealth of MSL experience will be a crown jewel for those without a doctorate.&nbsp;
The latitude to fill the MSL or Senior MSL level role is open, depending on the depth of your expertise.&nbsp;

&nbsp;
Join us if you're ready to be part of a vision that empowers patients and redefines the future of medicine. Please apply now for a chance to wield your expertise where it matters most, and be a part of a legacy in the making with Sense7ai Healthcare Division.&nbsp;


